Display Design File

library(DT)
dfDesign <- Obio@dfDesign
selVec <- c(
    'sampleID',
    'original.sample.id',
    'sample.id',
    'comp_1',
    'comp_2',
    'comp_3',
    'comp_4',
    'LRT_PE_SE',
    'LRT_Sox10_Neg'
)

dfDesign <- unique(dfDesign[,selVec])
colnames <- gsub("_", " ", names(dfDesign))
colnames <- gsub("comp", "DGE", colnames)
colnames <- gsub("[.]", " ", colnames)

datatable(
    dfDesign,
    colnames = colnames,
    rownames = FALSE
)

for (i in 1:length(Obio@scriptVec)){

}

Differential Gene Expression Plots

MAplots <- names(Obio@plotCollection)[grep("MA",names(Obio@plotCollection))]
Vplots <- gsub("MAplot_", "Volcano_Plot_", MAplots)


for (i in 1:length(MAplots)){
    pM <- Obio@plotCollection[[MAplots[i]]]
    pV <- Obio@plotCollection[[Vplots[i]]]
    print(
        ggarrange(
            pV,
            pM,
            nrow = 1,
            ncol = 2
        )
    )

}
